<H3> <TI>   British Arms Embargo Examined </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    British Arms Embargo Examined </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94AA0072C Tel Aviv HATZOFE in Hebrew 2 Jun 94 p 3 </F>
<F P=103> 94AA0072C </F>
<F P=104>  Tel Aviv HATZOFE </F>
<F P=105>  Hebrew </F>


