<H3> <TI>   Current Value of Alon Plan Questioned </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Current Value of Alon Plan Questioned </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94AA0072A YEDI'OT AHARONOT (24-Hour Supplement) in Hebrew 
1 Jun 94 p 5 </F>

<F P=103> 94AA0072A </F>
<F P=104>  YEDI'OT AHARONOT (24-Hour Supplement) </F>
<F P=105>  Hebrew </F>


