<H3> <TI>   India Tobacco Corporation Makes Global Emergence </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    India Tobacco Corporation Makes Global Emergence </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94AS0311I Bangalore DECCAN HERALD in English 27 May 94 p 13 </F>
<F P=103> 94AS0311I </F>
<F P=104>  Bangalore DECCAN HERALD </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
