May publishes on page 10 a 50-word unattributed article on the 
seizure of "four kg of cocaine in Salvador Mazza, Salta 
Province." It adds that a Border Police agent arrested two 
Bolivian women during an inspection of a bus heading to Cordoba 
Province. The drug was hidden in their clothes. 

