<H3> <TI>   Ship Carrying 17 Tonnes of Cannabis Resin Seized in North Sea </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Ship Carrying 17 Tonnes of Cannabis Resin Seized in North Sea </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94WD0361A London THE GUARDIAN in English 19 Apr 94 p 11--FOR 
